[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在“海姆达尔海岛运动会”结束之后，\\N我与猫汐尔便踏上了寻找谜之无人机的冒险。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过就在此时之前趁乱潜入控制中心的谜之无人机，\\N也成功接管了岛屿中控系统。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "随着岛屿被墙面分割成三片区域，\\N谜之无人机背后的操控者总算现身。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“寻找岛屿上残破的石板发掘香蒲族消失的秘密吧。”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "于是，我们被强行卷入了这样的调查游戏。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "香蒲族。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "大约距今两千年前被称为“香蒲族”的族群，\\N于今天的帕特拉地区西海岸出海。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在跨越了无数风暴与巨浪之后，\\N他们最终踏上了如今我们脚下的这片土地。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "由此他们开始在这座与世隔绝的小岛上，\\N建造起只属于他们的乐土。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但大概在一千三百年前，\\N这个文明却突然开始由盛转衰。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而所有的香蒲人也在某日突然“蒸发”……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "传言，他们集体前往了“另一个世界”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与瓦尔哈拉类似的，“精神世界”。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "随着游戏的推进除了香蒲族的真相外，\\N我们渐渐揭开了神秘人的面纱。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "安提克勒娅——\\N这位曾隶属于\"色雷斯\"卫城学院调查团的学者。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "过去她们曾经在这个小岛上，\\N展开过有关成年病起源的调查活动。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但当调查工作刚刚到了关键点，\\N即将破译开启遗迹中一扇密闭的石门时……却被学院叫停。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "拉美西斯集团与世界树公司便接管了这里，\\N世界树公司带走了所有的研究成果。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "色雷斯倾注所有的项目流产了，\\N卫城学院也撤回了她们的研究资金。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而安提克勒娅此番前来，正是想要借我们之手，\\N打开那扇密闭石门，拼凑齐最后的石板。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可惜她的算计终成泡影，\\N我们提前看穿了她诡计并设局将其擒获。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而至于香蒲族消失的真相则令人惋惜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那个被神秘瘟疫吞噬的族群，\\N如同今天的降临团一般。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "将未来寄托于虚无的神明，\\N丧失了再生活下去的勇气。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在虚构的谎言中，他们选择集体步入永恒的安眠，\\N用长眠逃避现实的苦难。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "事实也许并非全部如此。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在人类尚未彻底征服大洋的时代",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "满身伤痕，饱受战争摧残，从海岛另一端漂流至此的人们祈祷着",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "“让我们自此与世间苦痛诀别”",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "于是，在献上了无数祭品之后，\\N图拉卡斯终于给予了他们回应",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有痛觉的孩子降生了",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这便是第一位神使诞生的故事",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "——摘自安提克勒娅《雅卢岛风土见闻录》",
